        "Description": "The Sceptre allows rich and powerful criminals to hide from the authorities, which is why you are being sent in to deal with this problem.\r Your targets are:\r-Zana &quot;The Vulture&quot; Kazemi, a dangerous assasin.\r-Lucy Philips, an artist obsessed with Marcus Stuyvesant.\r-Cornelia Stuyvesant, a member of the dangerous Stuyvesant family.\r-Hans Lucht, a blackmailer.\r-Omar Al-Ghazali, the owner of The Sceptre itself.\rGood luck, agent.",
